<text name="event_LANIUS_DISTRESS_TRAP_text">You are too late - whatever once was emitting the distress signal from this system drew a Lanius ship as well as your own. Having consumed the original target, the Lanius turn their attention to your vessel. [ Lns SF DLR; S: 0.2, 3-4, RStuff; Esc: 0.2, 2-4 ]</text>
