<text name="text_FUEL_ON_MANTIS_ATTACK_2">Before long a ship jumps nearby, no doubt responding to your beacon. However any relief you felt disappears as soon as you recognize that the ship is of Mantis design. Prepare for a fight. [ Mts SF K: MScrapFuel, CK: HScrapFuel ]</text>
<text name="text_FUEL_ON_MANTIS_ATTACK_3">You detect a Mantis ship approaching and hack into their comm channel and hear, "...hope they put up more of a fight than the last Federation ship. This has been a disappointing day so far." Looks like they're not here to help. [ Mts SF K: MScrapFuel, CK: HScrapFuel ]</text>
