<text name="text_FUEL_ON_REBEL_ATTACK_1">A Rebel ship hails you, "Hello citizen. We are responding to your distress call and can assist... Wait a second... You're that ship! Prepare to die!" [ Rbl SF K: MScrapFuel, CK: HScrapFuel ]</text>
<text name="text_FUEL_ON_REBEL_ATTACK_2">A Rebel ship jumps nearby, "I wasn't looking forward to patrolling this boring sector but here you are, the most wanted ship in the area, just asking for me to find you. It looks like it's my lucky day!" They power up their weapons. [ Rbl SF K: MScrapFuel, CK: HScrapFuel ]</text>
