<text name="ship_REBEL_AUTO_WARNING_escape_text">The ship starts to power up its FTL Drive. If it gets away, it will no doubt warn the fleet of your position! [ Auto SF; Esc: 22-22, 40s, Fleet+; K: LStd ]</text>
<text name="ship_REBEL_ENGI_UNLOCK_2FAKE_escape_text">As soon as they see you, they power up their engines to jump away. Stop them! [ Rbl SF Esc: 18-18, 40s; K: MStd; CK: MStd (Decoy); HStd (Real) ]</text>
<text name="ship_REBEL_ENGI_UNLOCK_2REAL_escape_text">As soon as they see you they power up their engines to jump away. Stop them! [ Rbl SF Esc: 18-18, 40s; K: MStd; CK: MStd (Decoy); HStd (Real) ]</text>
<text name="ship_REBEL_HELPERS_SHIP_destroyed_c1_choice">Steal the civilian supplies. [ LScrapDrones | Nil | LScrap | -2 Hull ]</text>
<text name="ship_REBEL_HELPERS_SHIP_destroyed_c2_choice">Leave the civilians alone. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="ship_SLUG_DISTRESS_MANTIS_destroyed_c1_choice">Leave them be. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="ship_SLUG_DISTRESS_MANTIS_destroyed_c2_choice">Finish them off. [ LScrapAugment | RStd ]</text>
<text name="ship_SQUAT_PIRATE_MERCENARY_surrender_c1_choice">Let them live and then return to the settlement. [ MScrapWeapon ]</text>
<text name="ship_SQUAT_PIRATE_MERCENARY_surrender_c2_choice">Forget your promise, they die! [ K: LStd, CK: LStd ]</text>
<text name="ship_SQUAT_WARNING_escape_text">They are powering up their FTL! If they get away, they will no doubt warn the fleet of your position! [ Rbl SF K: MStd; CK: MStd; Esc: 22-22, 40s, Fleet+ ]</text>
<text name="ship_ZOLTAN_SCIENCE_DOCK_surrender_text">The Zoltan captain sends an urgent hail: "Wait, this was all a test! A test that you passed! A diverse crew, working together, surely a sight to warm the heart of any dispassionate observer. Come, I shall join your crew!" [ LStd, ZoltanCrew+ ]</text>

