<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_LIST_4_c2_choice">Scrap the machinery. [ LScrap ]</text>
<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_LIST_5_text">You dock with the station to take a look inside. However no sooner do you open the airlock than pirates burst in. Meanwhile scanners pick up a previously undetected pirate ship moving in to attack! [ Prt SF DR; 2 Boarders; S: 0.5, 3-4, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
