<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_c1_choice">Dock with the refueling platform. [ [ Fuel Trade | 3-5 Fuel | More... ] | [ [ -3 Hull, 2-4 Boarders | 5 Fuel BlastDoors BO ] | -3 Hull, Prt SF DR, -3 Hull; S: 0.5, 3-4, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 2-4 ] ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_c2_choice">Ignore the refueling platform. [ Nil | Prt SF DR; S: 0.5, 3-4, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_PIRATE_LIST_1_c1_choice">Wait for them to finish [ -3 Hull, 2-4 Boarders ].</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_PIRATE_LIST_1_c2_choice">(Blast Doors) Seal your blast doors, one can never be too careful when docked. [ +5 Fuel ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_PIRATE_LIST_2_text">The refueling station welcomes you into one of its berths, and as you hail them, there is an explosion from your engine room! While assessing the damage, you detect a Pirate Ship closing fast! [ Prt SF DR, -3 Hull; S: 0.5, 3-4, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_NORMAL_LIST_2_c1_choice">Steal it. [ +3-5 Fuel ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_NORMAL_LIST_2_c2_choice">War doesn't justify abandoning one's values. You leave it alone. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_NORMAL_LIST_3_c1_choice">Quickly dock and refuel. [ 5 Fuel | -3 Fuel, -3 Hull ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_NORMAL_LIST_3_c2_choice">Give the station a wide berth and carry on. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_HELP_MINERS_c1_c1_choice">Give them the requested 5 missiles. [ -5 Missiles, [ +15-25 scrap | +10 Hull | Reactor+1 ] ]</text>
<text name="event_HELP_MINERS_c1_c2_choice">Give them 15 missiles. [ -15 Missiles, [ +30-40 Scrap, +5 Hull | Reactor+1, +15 Hull | Random Augment ] ]</text>
<text name="event_HELP_MINERS_c1_c3_choice">Decline. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_HELP_MINERS_c1_choice">(Missile Weapon) Offer to solve their problem by launching a missile.</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_2_text">A complete scan of the planet reveals no life signs other than a single ship on the surface. The terraformers thank you for your help, and attempt to contact the ship. Just as you're about to jump away, the ship takes off and attacks, it's a pirate! [ Prt SF DR; S: 0.5, 3-4, RStuf; Esc: 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c1_choice">Tell them to stop. Any life is valuable. [ 15-25 Scrap or -15-25 Scrap for Oxygen +1 or Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c1_c1_choice">Accept the bribe and leave. [ 15-25 Scrap ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c1_c2_choice">Offer to pay them to at least delay until the mold can be studied. [ -15-25 Scrap, Oxygen +1 ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c1_c3_choice">Power your weapons and demand they leave at once. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c2_choice">Leave them to their work.</text>
<text name="event_PIRATE_SALESMAN_c1_choice">Hail the ship. [ More ... ]</text>
<text name="event_PIRATE_SALESMAN_c2_choice">Attack him before he can attack! [ Prt SF DR; S: 0.5, 3-4, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_PIRATE_SALESMAN_c3_choice">Quickly prepare to jump away. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c1_choice">Offer your help. [ 0-4 Missiles, 0-2 Drones, 2-4 Fuel, Construction Quest ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c2_choice">Decline. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c3_choice">(Lanius Crew) Offer to have your crewmember help. [ MScrap or HScrapAugment for Lanius trade ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c3_c1_c1_choice">Ask your crew if they agree. [ HScrapAugment, LaniusCrew- ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c3_c1_c2_choice">Our crew is not for sale. [ MScrap ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_1_c1_choice">Attack the Rebels to help them escape. [ Rbl SF Enemy ASB, K: MStd, CK: HStd, DB: MScrap ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_1_c2_choice">Leave. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_2_c1_choice">Move in to examine the station. [ Nil | x2 LScrap | [ LScrap | CloneBay BO [ x2 Crew+ | +1 Boarder ] ] | 2 Boarders, Prt SF DR | 2-4 Boarders, Enemy ASB ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_2_c2_choice">Stay near the Beacon. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_3_c1_choice">Give them the requested 4 fuel. [ MScrap, -4 Fuel ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_3_c2_choice">Give them 1 fuel. [ -1 Fuel ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_3_c3_choice">Do not give them any. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_CHECKPOINT_c1_choice">Fend for yourself, attack and escape. [ Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_CHECKPOINT_c2_choice">Bribe the Rebels to release the civilian ships. [ Nil | LScrap | LStd | Rbl SF DR ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_HELPERS_c1_choice">Attack the Rebels. [ Rbl SF K: LStd, CK: MStd, DB: Nil or [ LScrapDrones | Nil | LScrap | -2 Hull ] ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_HELPERS_c2_choice">Wait and steal the supplies from the civilians. [ LScrapDrones | Nil | LScrap | -2 Hull ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_HELPERS_c3_choice">Leave them be. [ Nil ]</text>
