<text name="event_REFUGEE_NO_DISTRESS_PIRATE_c2_choice">Ignore the refugees. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_NO_DISTRESS_SLUG_c1_choice">Hail them. [ Resource Trade | Prt SF K: MStd, CK: HStd, DB: LStd ]</text>
