<text name="event_REFUGEE_NO_DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_c2_choice">Ignore the refugees. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_ARGUMENT_NEBULA_c1_choice">Get closer. [ More... ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_ARGUMENT_NEBULA_c2_choice">Ignore them. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_ARGUMENT_c1_choice">Hail them to see what's wrong. [ More ... ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_ARGUMENT_c2_choice">Leave them be. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_ARGUMENT_c1_c1_choice">Offer to pay off the Rock debt. [ -10-15 Scrap, [ Nil | Reactor+1 | 10-15 Scrap Reactor Upgrade ] ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_ARGUMENT_c1_c2_choice">Demand the Rock ship pay the agreed upon price. [ -5 Hull | [ Nil | Reactor+1 | 10-15 Scrap Reactor Upgrade ] | Rck SF K: LStd, CK: MStd, DB: [ Nil | Reactor+1 | 10-15 Scrap Reactor Upgrade ] ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_ARGUMENT_c1_c3_choice">You have better things to attend to, leave them. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_COMMAND_1_text">Apparently the Rock Captain was more annoyed than you thought, they shut off all communication and turn on you, the 'slime balls' defender.' [ Rck SF K: LStd, CK: MStd, DB: [ Nil | Reactor+1 | 10-15 Scrap Reactor Upgrade ] ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_GRATEFUL_3_c1_choice">Agree to the price. [ Reactor+1, -10-15 Scrap ]</text>
<text name="event_ROCK_SLUG_GRATEFUL_3_c2_choice">Decline the offer. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_ROGUE_REBEL_c1_choice">Go looking for the Rebel ship. [ Nil | x2 Rbl SF DR | Rbl SF DR, Fleet+ ]</text>
<text name="event_ROGUE_REBEL_c2_choice">No time to search, you prepare to jump away. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_ROGUE_REBEL_c3_choice">(Improved Sensors) Perform a scan of the area. [ Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_ROGUE_REBEL_c4_choice">(Advanced Sensors) Pinpoint the Rebel's location. [ Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4; Enemy Engines@0 ]</text>
<text name="event_TERRAFORMING_SCAN_c1_c1_choice">Attempt to scan the planet. [ Nil | [ +1 Oxygen | Prt SF DR | More... ] ]</text>
<text name="event_TERRAFORMING_SCAN_c1_c2_choice">(Advanced Sensors) Set sensors to maximum and scan. [ +1 Oxygen | Prt SF DR | More... ]</text>
<text name="event_TERRAFORMING_SCAN_c1_c3_choice">(Zoltan) Send your crewman to overcharge their systems. [ +1 Oxygen | Prt SF DR | More... ]</text>
<text name="event_TERRAFORMING_SCAN_c2_choice">You do not have time. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_TRADER_UPGRADES_EXCHANGE_c1_choice">Agree to the trade. [ Reactor +1 ]</text>
<text name="event_TRADER_UPGRADES_EXCHANGE_c2_choice">Respectfully decline. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_WRECKAGE_EVENT_c1_choice">(Improved Sensors) Use your Sensors to scan the wreckage. [ MStuff ]</text>
<text name="event_WRECKAGE_EVENT_c2_choice">(Advanced Sensors) Use your Sensors to scan the wreckage. [ HStuff | LScrapWeapon ]</text>
<text name="event_WRECKAGE_EVENT_c3_choice">Investigate the battlefield. [ x5 Nil | MStuff | Mts SF DR | Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 | Ztn SF DR ]</text>
<text name="event_WRECKAGE_EVENT_c4_choice">Ignore the wreckage and continue on. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="event_WRECKAGE_INVESTIGATE_6_text">As you approach the wreckage, a Mantis ship screams into the system... either sensing prey - or to finish the job its fellows started. [ Mts SF DR ]</text>
<text name="event_WRECKAGE_INVESTIGATE_7_text">The wreckage appears to be a battle between Federation fighters and Rebel cruisers. Though outnumbered, it looks like the Federation fought valiantly. As you begin a more detailed scan of the wreckage, Rebel reinforcements arrive in the system and target your ship! [ Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_WRECKAGE_INVESTIGATE_8_text">As you approach the wreckage, a Zoltan ship makes its arrival. It immediately mistakes you for one of the attackers, declares you as hostile aggressors in violation of Zoltan space, and opens fire! [ Ztn SF DR ]</text>
<text name="text_GENERIC_HIDE_TEXT_1">Fly behind a moon and stay hidden. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="text_GENERIC_HIDE_TEXT_2">Shut down all non-vital systems and stay hidden. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="text_GENERIC_HIDE_TEXT_3">Stay quiet and hope they don't notice you. [ Nil ]</text>
<text name="text_GENERIC_HIDE_TEXT_4">Stay out of their way and charge your FTL drive. [ Nil ]</text>
